text: Heribert Karches (born 12 November 1958) is a German rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Mainz
